              "rotate": 0,
              "content": "<p style='font-size:12px;color:#94a3b8;line-height:1.8;'>Each candle shows: <b style='color:#f1f5f9;'>Open, High, Low, Close</b>. The body = range between open and close. Wicks = highest and lowest price touched. <b style='color:#10b981;'>Green</b> = closed higher. <b style='color:#f87171;'>Red</b> = closed lower.</p>",
