              "content": "<p style='font-size:11px;font-weight:800;color:#f59e0b;text-align:center;'>Doji</p><p style='font-size:10px;color:#94a3b8;text-align:center;margin-top:4px;line-height:1.6;'>Open ≈ Close. Buyers and sellers equally matched. Indecision — wait for confirmation.</p>",
