              "left": 524,
              "top": 118,
              "width": 440,
              "height": 28,
              "rotate": 0,
              "content": "<p style='font-size:14px;font-weight:800;color:#60a5fa;'>🎯 Support & Resistance</p>",
              "defaultFontName": "Inter",
              "defaultColor": "#60a5fa"
            },
            {
              "id": "hs-tr-s1-sr-b",
              "type": "text",
              "left": 524,
              "top": 148,
              "width": 440,
              "height": 195,
              "rotate": 0,
              "content": "<p style='font-size:12px;color:#94a3b8;line-height:1.9;'><b style='color:#34d399;'>Support:</b> Price zone where buying has historically stopped declines. Tested and held multiple times = stronger support. Buy near support, stop-loss just below.<br/><br/><b style='color:#f87171;'>Resistance:</b> Price zone where selling has historically capped rallies. Breaking through is bullish. Look to reduce near resistance, watch for breakout.<br/><br/><b style='color:#f59e0b;'>Role Reversal:</b> Old resistance becomes new support after a breakout — one of the most reliable TA patterns.</p>",
              "defaultFontName": "Inter",
              "defaultColor": "#94a3b8"
            },
