              }
            },
            {
              "id": "hs-tr-s2-rsi-h",
              "type": "text",
              "left": 34,
              "top": 118,
              "width": 430,
              "height": 26,
              "rotate": 0,
              "content": "<p style='font-size:13px;font-weight:800;color:#a78bfa;'>RSI — Relative Strength Index (0–100)</p>",
              "defaultFontName": "Inter",
              "defaultColor": "#a78bfa"
            },
            {
              "id": "hs-tr-s2-rsi-b",
              "type": "text",
              "left": 34,
              "top": 146,
              "width": 430,
              "height": 135,
              "rotate": 0,
              "content": "<p style='font-size:12px;color:#94a3b8;line-height:2;'>Measures overbought/oversold on 0–100 scale. Default 14-period lookback.<br/><b style='color:#f87171;'>RSI above 70</b> → Overbought, potential pullback<br/><b style='color:#34d399;'>RSI below 30</b> → Oversold, potential bounce<br/><b style='color:#f59e0b;'>RSI at 50</b> → Neutral, trend undecided<br/><i style='color:#64748b;'>Caveat: in strong trends, RSI stays extreme. Don't short just because RSI is 70.</i></p>",
              "defaultFontName": "Inter",
              "defaultColor": "#94a3b8"
            },
            {
              "id": "hs-tr-s2-macd-bg",
              "type": "shape",
              "left": 490,
              "top": 110,
              "width": 484,
              "height": 180,
              "rotate": 0,
              "path": "M 0 0 L 1 0 L 1 1 L 0 1 Z",
              "viewBox": [
                1,
                1
              ],
              "fill": "#3b82f610",
              "fixedRatio": false,
              "outline": {
                "style": "solid",
                "width": 1,
                "color": "#3b82f640"
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "hs-tr-s2-macd-h",
              "type": "text",
              "left": 500,
              "top": 118,
              "width": 464,
              "height": 26,
              "rotate": 0,
              "content": "<p style='font-size:13px;font-weight:800;color:#60a5fa;'>MACD — Moving Average Convergence Divergence</p>",
              "defaultFontName": "Inter",
              "defaultColor": "#60a5fa"
            },
            {
              "id": "hs-tr-s2-macd-b",
              "type": "text",
              "left": 500,
              "top": 146,
              "width": 464,
              "height": 135,
              "rotate": 0,
              "content": "<p style='font-size:12px;color:#94a3b8;line-height:2;'>Tracks difference between 12-period and 26-period EMAs. Signal line = 9-period EMA of MACD.<br/><b style='color:#34d399;'>Bullish cross:</b> MACD crosses above signal → buy signal<br/><b style='color:#f87171;'>Bearish cross:</b> MACD crosses below signal → sell signal<br/><b style='color:#a78bfa;'>Divergence:</b> Price new high but MACD doesn't → weakening momentum</p>",
              "defaultFontName": "Inter",
              "defaultColor": "#94a3b8"
            },
            {
              "id": "hs-tr-s2-orders-h",
              "type": "text",
              "left": 24,
              "top": 306,
              "width": 460,
              "height": 26,
              "rotate": 0,
              "content": "<p style='font-size:13px;font-weight:800;color:#f59e0b;'>⚡ Order Types</p>",
              "defaultFontName": "Inter",
              "defaultColor": "#f59e0b"
            },
            {
              "id": "hs-tr-s2-orders-b",
              "type": "text",
              "left": 24,
              "top": 334,
              "width": 460,
              "height": 130,
              "rotate": 0,
              "content": "<p style='font-size:12px;color:#94a3b8;line-height:2.1;'><b style='color:#f59e0b;'>Market:</b> Execute now at best price. Guaranteed fill, accept spread.<br/><b style='color:#3b82f6;'>Limit:</b> Only fill at your price or better. Not guaranteed.<br/><b style='color:#ef4444;'>Stop-Loss:</b> Auto-exit if price falls to your set level. Defines max loss.<br/><b style='color:#10b981;'>Take-Profit:</b> Auto-exit at target. Lock in gains without watching.<br/><b style='color:#a78bfa;'>R:R Ratio:</b> Risk $100 to make $200 = 1:2. Target min 1:2.</p>",
              "defaultFontName": "Inter",
              "defaultColor": "#94a3b8"
            },
            {
              "id": "hs-tr-s2-psych-bg",
